  "name": "Offline POS fails to uninstall",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"offline-pos-fails-to-uninstall\">Offline POS fails to uninstall</h1>\n<p><strong>If Offline POS fails to uninstall or gets stuck during the uninstall process and error messages occur, the following steps should help to uninstall correctly.</strong></p>\n<p><strong><span>This guide also helps to use straight away when uninstalling the Offline POS with or without errors/taking a long time, this will reduce heavily the amount of time to uninstall.</span></strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Agent-Only-Offline-POS-Troubleshooting\">By following the original steps from Offline POS Troubleshooting </a></p>\n<p>If this error messages appear during uninstall do <strong>NOT</strong> press <strong><span>Retry</span></strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T223232.792.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVgnEAE.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>press <strong><span>Cancel</span></strong> and continue<br/> </p>\n<hr></hr><p>The following steps should fix the issue</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ol><li>Open Task Manager and <strong>END TASK </strong>for :\n<pre class=\"code codeBlock\" spellcheck=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><br/>REX.Offline.UpdateService (32 bit)</pre>\n<pre class=\"code codeBlock\" spellcheck=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><br/>REX.Offline.PosService (32 bit)</pre>\n<p><strong><span>End all tasks that start with '</span><span>REX.Offline</span><span>'</span></strong><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T223238.838.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVhWEAU.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n\t</li><li>Press Retry or proceed to uninstall Offline POS</li><li>Offline POS should uninstall correctly with a finish button</li><li>Press Okay if messages appear during the uninstall</li></ol><p><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T223244.121.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppVjrEAE.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>",
